{"word":"ὑπερμάχομαι","slug":"ὑπερμάχομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑπερμάχομαι</b></el> <p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> = <a href='S:ὑπερμαχέω'><el>ὑπερμαχέω</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>; <el>τάδ' πατρὸς ὑπερμαχοῦμαι</el> <i>will fight</i> this <i>battle for</i> him, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}